description.en:
Luna toy kitchen

Become a star in the kitchen with this stylish play kitchen! The kitchen features a hood, oven, faucet, utensils and many food products. Furthermore, there are fun light and sound effects in this kitchen, so children will be entertained for hours.

Luna spielzeug küche

Material: Kunststoff
